"763","<p align=center style=line-height:150%;margin-bottom:.0001pt;margin-left:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-top:0in;text-align:center;><font face=Calibri,sans-serif lang=EN-US style=font-size:11.0pt;>&nbsp;</font></p>"
"764","<p style=line-height:150%;margin-bottom:.0001pt;margin-left:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-top:0in;><font face=Calibri,sans-serif lang=EN-US style=font-size:11.0pt;>Item 77D: Policies with respect to securities investments:</font></p>"
"765","<p style=line-height:150%;margin-bottom:.0001pt;margin-left:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-top:0in;><font face=Calibri,sans-serif lang=EN-US style=font-size:11.0pt;>Effective November 15, 2013, the following changes occurred in the"
